stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> initial: createDenialTrackingState()
    initial --> tracking: 首次记录

    tracking --> tracking: recordDenial(+1/+1)
    tracking --> tracking: recordSuccess(重置consecutive)

    tracking --> fallback_consecutive: consecutive >= 3
    tracking --> fallback_total: total >= 20

    fallback_consecutive --> tracking: 用户审核后继续
    fallback_total --> reset: 用户审核后重置
    reset --> tracking: totalDenials归零
